  m_text: 'Left Mouse Button: Sword Swing.

    Middle Mouse Button: Fire Grappling
    Hook.

    Right Mouse Button: Lift Shield.

    Kill the required mob count
    and the boss to finish the game.

    The game might not actually finish at this
    time.

    Press esc to quit the game, p to pause.

    Green Bars are DOORS,
    travel through them to the next area

    Green Circles are Grapple Points.'
